      "tool_title": "Final QA Release Certificate",
      "activity_name": "QA Release",
      "tier": "both",
      "notes": "Issued when all D9.2, D9.3, D9.4 checks pass (and any D9.6 rework is re-inspected and closed). Formally releases the unit from QA hold. Unlocks D9.8.",
